[[File:Muammar_al-Gaddafi-30112006.jpg|thumb]]，並提倡「[[非洲合眾國|非洲合眾國]]」的理念<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oocities.org/~dagmawi/News/News_Sep17_Gadhafi.html|title=Libya's Gaddafi turns attention to black Africa<!-- Bot generated title -->|publisher=|accessdate=2018-10-27|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111084937/http://www.oocities.org/~dagmawi/News/News_Sep17_Gadhafi.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www2.orlandoweekly.com/news/story.asp?id=942|title=Orlandoweekly.com – COLUMNS: Brand recognition<!-- Bot generated title -->|publisher=|accessdate=2018-10-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.libyanet.com/1098nwsc.htm|title=Libya: News and Views|website=www.libyanet.com|accessdate=2018-10-27|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111084945/http://www.libyanet.com/1098nwsc.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1998/oct/02/news/mn-28652|title=Kadafi Lambastes Arab Allies' Stance in Pan Am Blast Case|first=JOHN|last=DANISZEWSKI|date=1998-10-02|publisher=|accessdate=2018-10-27|via=LA Times|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308191628/http://articles.latimes.com/1998/oct/02/news/mn-28652|dead-url=no}}</ref>]]
